 Speaking as one of the wizards in line for a VS staff in my guild all i can do here is waiting for the others to get it and while I am always happy when one of my guildmates gets his staff I find it rather frustrating that there is nothing I can do about this myself, but to make sure that i am present for the VS raids.<br>
